1. To starom kućom se vezuju mnoge uspomene. (Many memories are linked to the old house.) 
2. Starom se čoveku nije dalo da priča. (The old man couldn't talk.) 
3. Ona je starome čoveku pomogla. (She helped the old man.) 
4. Starome ocu smo uvek bili odani. (We were always loyal to the old father.) 
5. Starom drvetu je trebalo obrezivanje. (The old tree needed pruning.)